creator: LULU DELIVERY LIMITED
descriptionHtml:
Order anything you want with LULU and it will be delivered in minutes. You can order from any restaurant in your city, or from any supermarket and shop.
Food, pharmacy, flowers, groceries, games, socks, your favorite burger, pizza, Goiko grill, kebab, tapas, sushi… we can go and pick up your suit from the dry cleaners or bring you the keys you’ve forgotten. You order, and LULU gets it for you.
Find great deals nearby. Save time and money. Enjoy 24/7 delivery service. Anything, anywhere.
